title: Ep 36: The New Jeff Dunham
description:
Today's proceedings:  A man discovers his girlfriend's talents as a new Jeff Dunham using her "lady parts," a kid poops himself whenever he doesn't get his way, and we talk about some female anatomy in the nether regions.  We also "clap back" to some haters, and discuss how Zoomers HATE millennial trends.
